      <p>Ruby on Rails for Personal Projects<br/> HTML + CSS + Javascript</p><br/>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4"> 
      <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/stxts-profile/csharp.png" class="img-rounded margin" alt="Image" height="300" width="300">
      <p>C# .NET MVC for Work<br/>Visual Studio</p><br/>
